    <div id="content">
       <section>
       		<h2>Histogram View</h2>
         <img src="annoControlsFits.png">
         <p>The histogram view gadget allows you to construct a histogram from one specific field of a data set.
         The data is automatically displayed after selecting a data set, x axis and number of bins.
         <p>Selecting a specific block of the histogram selects all of the points within that region. If there 
         are any points within a block that are selected, the entire bin will appear to be selected.
         <ul>
         	<li><a href="gadgets.html">Return to gadgets index</a></li>
         <lu>
